label: uncl1373
comment: Code specifying the status of a document.

values.label: Accepted
values.comment: The specified document is accepted.

values.label: Accompanying goods
values.comment: Notice that a specific document will be accompanying the goods.

values.label: Conditionally accepted
values.comment: The specified document is conditionally accepted.

values.label: To arrive by separate EDI message
values.comment: Notice that a specific document/message will be transmitted via a separate EDI message.

values.label: Information only
values.comment: Notice that the specific document or message is for information only.

values.label: To arrive by manual means
values.comment: Notice that a specific document or message will not be sent via EDI.

values.label: To be raised and sent
values.comment: Request for a specific message to be formatted and transmitted or a request for a specific document to be raised and sent.

values.label: Rejected
values.comment: The specified document is rejected.

values.label: To be printed
values.comment: The document or message is to be printed.

values.label: Document currently valid
values.comment: Specific document is currently valid.

values.label: Document not available
values.comment: Specified document is not available.

values.label: Document exhausted by declaration and attached
values.comment: Customs declaration to which the document is related completed or exhaust the allowance stated on the document. The document is attached to the Customs declaration.

values.label: Document not exhausted by declaration and attached
values.comment: Customs declaration to which the document is related does not complete or exhaust the allowance stated on the document . The document is not attached to the declaration but has already been lodged in the Customs station.

values.label: Document exhausted by declaration and previously lodged
values.comment: Customs declaration to which the document is related completed or exhaust the allowance stated on the document. The usage of the document is complete. The document is not attached to the declaration but has already been lodged in the Customs station.

values.label: Document not exhausted by declaration and previously lodged
values.comment: Customs declaration to which the document is related does not complete or exhaust the allowance stated on the document. The document can continue to be used for future declarations until the allowance is exhausted. The document is not attached to the declaration but has already been lodged in the Customs station.

values.label: Document not attached
values.comment: Specified document is not or cannot be attached.

values.label: Document with the goods
values.comment: Document not attached to the Customs declaration but is attached to the goods.

values.label: Document attached, to be returned after endorsement
values.comment: Specified document is attached to the Customs declaration and will be required to be returned to the declarant after Customs endorsement.

values.label: Document applied for
values.comment: Application has been submitted for that document.

values.label: Received for shipment
values.comment: Indicates that the document has legal validity from the date of receival of the cargo.

values.label: Shipped on board
values.comment: Indicates that the document has legal validity from the date that cargo is loaded on board a vessel.

values.label: Status 0
values.comment: Message is at status 0.

values.label: Status 1
values.comment: Message is at status 1.

values.label: Status 2
values.comment: Message is at status 2.

values.label: Message under development
values.comment: Message is under development.

values.label: Document not freighted
values.comment: Document not to include freight figures.

values.label: Document freighted
values.comment: Document to include freight figures.

values.label: Archived
values.comment: The document or message has been archived.

values.label: Provisional
values.comment: The document or message has no official status.

values.label: Documents enclosed in the first transmission
values.comment: The documents are enclosed in the first transmission.

values.label: Documents enclosed in the second transmission
values.comment: The documents are enclosed in the second transmission.

values.label: Document not required, waiver issued
values.comment: The document is not required, waiver of requirement has been issued.

values.label: Already on file with receiver of this message
values.comment: The document is already on file with the party receiving the message.

values.label: Retained by sender of this message, or by sender's agent or representative
values.comment: The document is in the possession of the sender or sender's agent or representative.

values.label: Document incomplete
values.comment: The document is incomplete.

values.label: Document previously submitted
values.comment: The document has already been submitted.

values.label: Document complete
values.comment: The document is complete.

values.label: Final
values.comment: The document has been finalised.

values.label: On hold
values.comment: The document or message will not be processed until further release information.

values.label: Validity suspended
values.comment: The validity of the document is or has been suspended.

values.label: Validity revoked
values.comment: The validity of the document is or has been revoked.

values.label: In error
values.comment: The specified document is in error.

values.label: Received
values.comment: The document is received.

values.label: Accepted with warnings
values.comment: The document is accepted, but has generated warnings.
